long_description: bay travel specialise in executive coach hire and bus services and can offer one time hire as well as medium to long term contracts, with a range of daily services throughout fife, as well as excursion hire for airport transfers, golf tours, shopping trips, weddings and more. founded in 2008, bay travel executive coach hire has grown to become one of scotland's premier coach travel providers, growing from a staff of 2 to over 60. bay travel now provide local bus services, school bus services along with private hire & touring. give us a call to find out more about bay travel coach hire. we operate ten local bus routes in east fife with routes covering kirkcaldy, cowdenbeath, kelty, north queensferry and dunfermline. with bay you can hire executive level coaches for any kind of event. whether you have a day trip or you want to book a larger multi day trip, we can provide the coach to suit your needs for wedding day travel, airport transfers, corporate events, excursions and multi day trips.
